        {
            "title": "在南京大屠殺死難者國家公祭儀式上 中國就日本軍國主義發出警告",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 在周六舉行的南京大屠殺死難者國家公祭儀式上，中國就日本<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:軍國主義;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/軍國主義\">軍國主義</a>死灰復燃發出警告，但在兩國緊張局勢升級之際，中國並未直接批評日本領導人。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在南京舉行的儀式上，中共中央政治局委員<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:石泰峰;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/石泰峰\">石泰峰</a>回顧了1937年12月日軍攻占南京的慘況。他說，在中國共產黨的領導下，中國打敗了日本侵略者，成為了一個偉大的國家。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">石泰峰表示，任何企圖復活「軍國主義」、挑戰戰後國際秩序的行徑都將失敗。雖然他沒有提及日本首相高市早苗的名字，但這很可能是指中國的一種觀點，即她推動加強國防反映了她想要恢復日本過去的軍國主義政策。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-f9beb625-d0bb-342f-95d1-bc075c10d7a1-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">石泰峰在約8,000人參加的儀式上說道，「歷史已經證明，並將繼續證明，任何企圖復活軍國主義，挑戰戰後國際秩序，破壞世界和平穩定的行徑都注定要失敗。」</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題China Warns Against Japanese Militarism at Massacre Memorial</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Tian Ying.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%9C%A8%E5%8D%97%E4%BA%AC%E5%A4%A7%E5%B1%A0%E6%AE%BA%E6%AD%BB%E9%9B%A3%E8%80%85%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%B6%E5%85%AC%E7%A5%AD%E5%84%80%E5%BC%8F%E4%B8%8A-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%B0%B1%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E8%BB%8D%E5%9C%8B%E4%B8%BB%E7%BE%A9%E7%99%BC%E5%87%BA%E8%AD%A6%E5%91%8A-090854440.html",
